    "title": "Fix cloche loop ignoring config concurrency setting",
    "description": "cloche loop used max_concurrency=1 for shandalar even though config had orchestration.concurrency=2. The config key we read (loop.concurrency) doesn't match the key the user set (orchestration.concurrency). Align to use the existing config key.",
